snippet.description:
A work-in-progress walk through and preview for my upcoming game CONCRETE, releasing on Steam later this year. Still a lot more work to do and much is subject to change, but this should give a general idea of where I am at presently. More left to showcase, but that will be for a later date.

Maps featured will be included the free demo. The full release will have it's own polished, dense, and interactive set of story-rich levels.

